OL,7,FThe families of three teenagers who
OL,8,Fwere killed after a crash near
OL,9,FDumfries have been awarded a six-
OL,10,Ffigure sum in compensation.
OL,12,FJake Loy from Moffat was 17 when he
OL,13,Flost control and crashed into another
OL,14,Fcar on the A711 outside Dumfries in
OL,15,FMarch 2022.
