OL,7,FLast year, Loy was jailed for four
OL,8,Fyears and eight months and banned from
OL,9,Fdriving for eight years for causing
OL,10,Fthe deaths of Ian Cannon, Finlay Johns
OL,11,Fand Tyler Johnston by dangerous
OL,12,Fdriving.
OL,14,FA statement issued by the families'
OL,15,Fsolicitor, Digby Brown, said: "This
OL,16,Fwas a truly devastating collision `
OL,17,Fthree sons were lost in an avoidable
OL,18,Fcrash which resulted in life-changing
OL,19,Fand profound trauma to multiple
OL,20,Ffamilies.
